Sir wake up.

28:26.590 --> 28:27.880
<i>Keep this in mind.</i>

28:29.590 --> 28:32.680
<i>"Whether it be a grain of sand</i>
<i>or a rock...</i>

28:33.680 --> 28:37.270
<i>..in water they both sink alike. "</i>

28:43.820 --> 28:45.320
Are you awake?

28:55.830 --> 28:57.290
Is all this true?

29:18.770 --> 29:20.560
That fever remedy works well.

29:22.480 --> 29:26.020
Why did you faint if you've done
so much physical training?

29:28.030 --> 29:33.660
A lack of vital sunlight leaves one
depleted of vitamins A and E.

29:35.830 --> 29:38.660
Thus one's immunity to influenza
is weakened.

29:41.080 --> 29:42.960
Do you always talk like that?

29:56.180 --> 29:58.970
The lock on the bathroom door
is broken.

29:59.140 --> 30:00.640
Don't get any bright ideas

30:00.810 --> 30:02.730
or I'll gut you like a fish.

30:05.150 --> 30:06.190
What's this?

30:07.270 --> 30:11.400
Suppositories. You fainted so
how else could I give you medicine?

30:26.500 --> 30:30.920
<i>Can 15 years' worth of</i>
<i>imaginary training be put to use?</i>

30:39.010 --> 30:40.140
<i>Apparently not.</i>

30:56.320 --> 30:58.240
That was an unforgivable sin.

31:02.370 --> 31:06.750
I brought you back here
and then turned you down.

31:07.580 --> 31:09.170
I can see why you're angry.

31:10.340 --> 31:11.590
I really can.

31:15.170 --> 31:19.180
You know I brought you here
because I like you.

31:20.100 --> 31:21.260
But...

31:24.020 --> 31:26.100
You don't even know my name yet.

31:27.150 --> 31:28.310
It's Mido.

31:29.900 --> 31:31.110
You see...

31:32.730 --> 31:33.940
..later on...

31:35.650 --> 31:37.360
..when I'm really ready...

31:38.780 --> 31:41.490
..I swear on my life
that I'll go through with it.

31:43.080 --> 31:46.710
That song in your diary <i>The Face</i>
<i>I Want to See</i>  that will be the sign.

31:47.460 --> 31:49.170
When I sing it

31:49.330 --> 31:52.340
get ready.

31:54.380 --> 31:58.510
I may try to resist you again

31:58.680 --> 32:00.890
in the heat of the moment.

32:01.930 --> 32:04.350
But no matter what don't stop.

32:04.520 --> 32:07.350
Just give it to me!

32:09.980 --> 32:11.150
Give it...

32:13.070 --> 32:14.530
..to me.

32:20.360 --> 32:21.910
The ants...

32:23.080 --> 32:24.450
Do you still see them?

32:25.660 --> 32:27.290
Do you still feel that way?

32:29.080 --> 32:32.420
Yeah if you're alone you see ants.

32:33.590 --> 32:38.720
People I have met who are very lonely
have all hallucinated about ants.

32:40.340 --> 32:42.350
I tried once to work out why.

32:42.510 --> 32:45.470
Ants move around in groups
you know.

32:46.470 --> 32:50.480
So I suppose very lonely people
keep thinking of ants.

32:51.940 --> 32:54.400
Although I have never done that.

33:57.300 --> 34:00.340
<i>She called from overseas</i>
<i>five or six years ago</i>

34:00.510 --> 34:02.300
<i>asking if her dad had come back.</i>

34:03.090 --> 34:07.010
<i>She doesn't even know</i>
<i>that he killed her mother.</i>

34:07.560 --> 34:11.020
She has hardly any relatives
so she calls us.

34:12.389 --> 34:14.810
Her Korean has got worse.

34:16.610 --> 34:19.570
I think her Swedish foster parents
are both doctors.

34:22.739 --> 34:24.449
You journalists must know...

34:27.159 --> 34:29.239
Dae-su...

34:29.409 --> 34:31.909
Is he really still on the run?

34:36.170 --> 34:39.090
Your daughter's address
is on the front

34:39.250 --> 34:41.840
and on the back is a map of
your wife's grave.

34:45.800 --> 34:46.840
<i>Eva...</i>

34:47.800 --> 34:49.060
<i>Stockholm...</i>

34:49.850 --> 34:50.770
<i>Eva...</i>

34:52.350 --> 34:53.810
Do you want to call her?

35:01.150 --> 35:02.610
Shall I call her?

35:08.620 --> 35:10.700
Shall we visit the grave tomorrow?

35:17.290 --> 35:21.300
<i>No first I have to kill</i>
<i>that bastard.</i>

35:48.200 --> 35:49.950
BLUE DRAGON

35:52.240 --> 35:53.660
Well?

35:53.830 --> 35:55.910
<i>I haven't tasted it yet.</i>

35:57.620 --> 35:59.750
BLUE DRAGON

36:02.210 --> 36:03.250
So?

36:05.050 --> 36:06.550
Did it taste the same?

36:20.020 --> 36:22.770
<i>I could taste food from</i>
<i>100 restaurants...</i>

36:25.150 --> 36:28.150
<i>..but I will never forget</i>
<i>the food I tasted for 15 years.</i>

36:35.750 --> 36:36.790
BLUE DRAGON

36:56.560 --> 36:59.020
Shall I create an ID for you
so you can log in?

36:59.770 --> 37:02.230
Do you have
a favourite film or song?

37:03.980 --> 37:08.030
I've already been talking...

37:09.280 --> 37:10.860
..to him...

37:17.870 --> 37:19.580
"The Count of Monte Cristo"?

37:21.790 --> 37:27.090
There's no one by that name here.

37:36.600 --> 37:39.140
HOW'S LIFE IN A BIGGER PRISON
OH DAE-SU?

37:39.430 --> 37:40.520
Who are you?

37:43.900 --> 37:46.820
Who are you?

37:47.980 --> 37:50.070
THE LONELY PRINCE IN THE HIGH
TOWER.

37:50.240 --> 37:51.280
Who is he?

37:56.950 --> 37:59.950
I don't know who he is.
I just chat to him sometimes.

38:00.660 --> 38:02.290
We talk about sushi.

38:12.550 --> 38:13.800
Where are you going?

38:21.890 --> 38:22.980
Where are you going?

38:23.390 --> 38:24.850
You are not to be trusted.

38:41.580 --> 38:43.580
- VIOL...
- BLUE DRAGON

38:43.790 --> 38:48.670
<i>Violet Blue Dragon...</i>
<i>What does that mean?</i>

39:01.350 --> 39:03.850
<i>Why did they order</i>
<i>from a place so far away?</i>

39:05.350 --> 39:07.980
<i>I've already passed</i>
<i>five Chinese restaurants.</i>

39:10.730 --> 39:13.360
<i>I think my lungs are</i>
<i>on the verge of exploding.</i>

39:20.240 --> 39:22.330
You there tell your cooks

39:22.500 --> 39:24.790
to put less scallions
in the dumplings.

39:26.290 --> 39:27.290
OK.

39:38.510 --> 39:40.300
- Leave it there and go.
- Yes sir.

40:18.090 --> 40:21.930
We don't take on anyone
who uses bodyguards.

40:22.100 --> 40:24.220
Some companies specialize in that.

40:25.140 --> 40:26.640
You should go to them.

40:27.560 --> 40:30.350
We just take the small fry.

40:31.610 --> 40:35.360
If the stay is over six months
transportation is free.

40:36.070 --> 40:38.110
Yes of course.

40:44.620 --> 40:46.410
Why did you imprison me you...

40:49.120 --> 40:50.830
..dickshit.

40:52.540 --> 40:55.250
In our business on floor 7½

40:56.460 --> 40:59.260
client confidentiality
is our livelihood.

41:17.650 --> 41:20.360
I am going to avenge myself
for all 15 years.

41:21.610 --> 41:24.780
Each tooth I extract
will age you by one year.

41:41.130 --> 41:42.180
Keep still.

41:49.980 --> 41:51.270
Do you want to talk?

42:13.120 --> 42:15.130
I don't know...

42:15.290 --> 42:18.000
I didn't see his face...

42:18.170 --> 42:20.880
I made recordings...

42:34.810 --> 42:36.310
OH DAE-SU

42:42.280 --> 42:44.990
All those who are blood-type AB
raise your hand.

42:58.090 --> 43:00.630
Go. Shoo!
He has lost a lot of blood.

43:53.770 --> 43:54.930
Piece of shit.

44:00.150 --> 44:01.650
Is he dead?

46:31.130 --> 46:32.800
<i>I can't seem to</i>

46:33.430 --> 46:35.800
<i>get through today either.</i>

46:37.560 --> 46:41.230
<i>Now I have become a monster.</i>

46:42.810 --> 46:44.730
<i>When my vengeance is over...</i>

46:46.020 --> 46:47.860
<i>..can I return to Oh Dae-su?</i>

46:53.650 --> 46:56.660
Mister are you alright?

46:56.820 --> 46:59.700
Look at all this blood.

46:59.870 --> 47:02.910
What happened to you?

47:08.420 --> 47:11.670
Saewoon Apartments Eung-am
building 8. Take care of him.

47:13.090 --> 47:14.130
Thank you.

47:15.010 --> 47:16.340
Not at all.

47:17.260 --> 47:19.260
Well then...

47:20.600 --> 47:21.850
Farewell Oh Dae-su.

47:25.850 --> 47:26.900
<i>Farewell...</i>

47:28.690 --> 47:30.270
<i>..Oh Dae-su.</i>

47:31.400 --> 47:32.440
<i>Farewell.</i>

47:34.400 --> 47:35.610
<i>Farewell.</i>

48:32.590 --> 48:34.760
<i>The bastard you hate</i>
<i>but don't dare kill.</i>

48:34.920 --> 48:38.050
<i>The bitch you detest</i>
<i>who deserves a fate worse than death.</i>

48:38.220 --> 48:39.800
<i>We are at your service.</i>

48:41.100 --> 48:44.100
<i>Won't he go crazy</i>
<i>if he's locked up for a long time?</i>

48:44.270 --> 48:49.310
<i>Well if you don't want that</i>
<i>we can drug his drinks.</i>

48:49.480 --> 48:52.480
<i>There's a thing</i>
<i>called 'Risterdal solution'.</i>

48:52.650 --> 48:56.150
<i>It's a reliable drug</i>
<i>used to treat schizophrenia.</i>

48:57.070 --> 49:00.280
<i>But it depends on the length</i>
<i>of the treatment</i>

49:00.450 --> 49:03.080
<i>so how long will he...</i>

49:03.240 --> 49:04.290
<i>15 years.</i>

49:06.500 --> 49:07.830
<i>Is that possible?</i>

49:08.000 --> 49:09.920
<i>What did he do?</i>

49:10.630 --> 49:12.210
<i>Oh Dae-su you see...</i>

49:13.540 --> 49:15.590
<i>..talks too much.</i>

49:17.970 --> 49:19.010
Go to sleep.

49:20.220 --> 49:23.430
Tomorrow you will visit
Joo-hwan's internet cafe.

49:33.770 --> 49:35.780
Sit wherever you like.

49:38.110 --> 49:39.150
Joo-hwan.

49:51.040 --> 49:52.500
<i>Oh Dae-su you see...</i>

49:53.710 --> 49:55.040
<i>..talks too much.</i>

49:59.550 --> 50:01.630
Have you heard this voice before?

50:02.680 --> 50:04.850
Who loathes me this much?

50:12.310 --> 50:14.690
Those 260 women you've had...

50:14.860 --> 50:18.940
I don't know the names
of their husbands...

50:19.150 --> 50:22.490
LOGON: MONSTER

50:28.370 --> 50:30.000
MIDO.

50:32.580 --> 50:34.250
Who's Mido?

50:34.420 --> 50:36.290
A little girl who cries a lot.

50:40.670 --> 50:41.720
Joo-hwan...

50:44.680 --> 50:45.720
Did I...

50:46.890 --> 50:48.560
..really talk too much?

50:52.350 --> 50:53.440
My friend...

50:53.600 --> 50:55.940
Maybe you should...

50:57.230 --> 51:01.490
..look for the criminal
among people you're close to.

51:04.110 --> 51:06.910
SEARCH: EVERGREEN

51:12.660 --> 51:13.710
CHAT TO EVERGREEN?

51:18.380 --> 51:22.220
CONGRATULATIONS YOUR CASE WAS
AUTOMATICALLY DISMISSED
YESTERDAY.

51:22.420 --> 51:24.180
But please remember this...

51:24.840 --> 51:26.050
Open quote.

51:27.970 --> 51:31.020
Like a gazelle
from the hand of the hunter...

51:31.180 --> 51:34.270
Like a bird
from the snare of the fowler...

51:35.480 --> 51:36.940
Free yourself.

51:40.860 --> 51:42.280
Close quote.

51:43.690 --> 51:45.780
Who are you? You bastard!

51:47.200 --> 51:49.330
<i>I decided when I was a prisoner</i>

51:49.490 --> 51:51.830
<i>that if I got out</i>
<i>I would trust no one.</i>

51:52.500 --> 51:54.870
<i>If I met anyone suspicious</i>

51:55.040 --> 51:57.750
<i>I would invent a secret</i>
<i>only known to the two of us.</i>

51:59.290 --> 52:02.420
That ID Monster is a trap
I designed to catch him.

52:03.550 --> 52:06.090
You let a stranger into your home.
Who are you?

52:16.730 --> 52:17.940
Who's Evergreen?

52:25.950 --> 52:29.950
<i>I tracked down that Evergreen ID</i>
<i>and found the owner's details.</i>

52:30.120 --> 52:32.490
- <i>Are you ready to jot it down?</i>
- Go ahead.

52:32.700 --> 52:35.910
<i>It's Su Dae-oh.</i>
<i>Does the surname 'Su' even exist?</i>

52:36.080 --> 52:39.710
- Address?
- <i>Saewoon Apartments in Eung-am.</i>

52:39.880 --> 52:41.380
<i>Building 7 flat 407.</i>

52:46.470 --> 52:48.430
<i>Actually life in a bigger prison</i>

52:48.590 --> 52:50.890
<i>does not suit me very well.</i>

53:09.610 --> 53:10.910
Evergreen.

53:12.780 --> 53:13.990
Who are you?

53:18.750 --> 53:20.420
Is that what you wanted to ask?

53:22.040 --> 53:25.000
No. You must find that out
for yourself.

53:25.170 --> 53:26.550
Come on it's a game.

53:27.470 --> 53:30.510
First " who?"
Then "why?"

53:31.590 --> 53:33.810
When you know the answer
come and see me.

53:34.180 --> 53:35.810
I'll mark your work.

53:35.970 --> 53:37.890
You have until July 5th.

53:39.980 --> 53:42.360
Oh no only five days left.

53:45.110 --> 53:46.150
Too short?

53:47.400 --> 53:48.860
Chin up.

53:49.030 --> 53:52.200
If you succeed
I'll kill myself instead of Mido.

53:55.620 --> 53:57.080
That's right Mido.

53:57.790 --> 53:59.620
I'm going to kill

53:59.790 --> 54:02.210
every woman you love until you die.

54:04.290 --> 54:05.670
Well you're notorious

54:05.840 --> 54:07.960
for not protecting your women anyway.

54:14.970 --> 54:18.270
Wow you're strong Mr Monster.

54:19.390 --> 54:21.640
Yes you are the monster
that I created.

54:24.270 --> 54:25.980
But you will never

54:26.150 --> 54:28.570
find out why
if you go through with this.

54:29.240 --> 54:31.490
You have been curious for 15 years...

54:32.240 --> 54:33.950
Are you still going to kill me?

54:43.620 --> 54:44.750
Sit down there.

54:52.130 --> 54:54.390
Ah the tooth torture!

54:56.260 --> 54:58.010
You won't have enough time.

54:59.100 --> 55:01.980
I have a pacemaker
for my weak heart.

55:03.100 --> 55:04.310
When it was put in...

55:06.360 --> 55:08.570
..do you know
what I said to the doctor?

55:11.860 --> 55:13.280
"Dr Hopkins

55:13.910 --> 55:15.240
give me...

55:16.530 --> 55:18.790
..a remote control
to turn my motor off."

55:19.200 --> 55:21.580
"Pardon? Why?"

55:24.420 --> 55:28.340
"So that I can kill myself. Easily.
At any time."

55:29.630 --> 55:32.170
"I'll pay you an extra $100000
for this."

55:47.310 --> 55:49.020
What a dilemma.

55:49.190 --> 55:52.110
You want to kill me right now

55:52.280 --> 55:54.900
but then you won't know
why you were imprisoned.

55:55.990 --> 55:59.580
You want to torture me
but I say I'll kill myself first.

56:01.950 --> 56:05.370
Revenge? Or the truth?

56:07.630 --> 56:10.340
What a problem for you.

56:11.090 --> 56:13.970
I've been watching over you
for 15 years.

56:16.220 --> 56:18.140
I've faired well thanks to you.

56:18.550 --> 56:21.930
I wasn't bored or lonely.

56:24.810 --> 56:28.730
Seeking revenge is the best cure
for someone who has been hurt.

56:28.900 --> 56:30.020
Try it.

56:31.940 --> 56:34.190
The loss of 15 years

56:35.070 --> 56:37.660
the pain of losing
your wife and child

56:37.820 --> 56:40.120
all this can be forgotten.

56:40.740 --> 56:44.500
Once again
revenge is good for your health.

56:45.120 --> 56:46.000
But...

56:47.620 --> 56:50.170
What happens
after you've had your revenge?

56:51.420 --> 56:54.880
I bet that hidden pain
probably emerges again.

56:58.300 --> 56:59.890
Are you there Oh Dae-su?

57:02.180 --> 57:03.350
Oh Dae-su.

57:04.390 --> 57:05.680
Long time no see.

57:14.900 --> 57:18.400
Hasn't she been tied up too long?
You left her door open.

57:32.340 --> 57:33.800
Save me Dae-su!

57:36.260 --> 57:37.800
<i>I can't. I'm going to die.</i>

57:47.980 --> 57:49.690
This dentist is very good.

57:58.570 --> 57:59.700
Keep still.

57:59.990 --> 58:02.160
Keep still.

58:03.280 --> 58:04.410
What's his problem?

58:33.480 --> 58:34.980
You see...

58:36.480 --> 58:38.570
..they say that people

58:39.360 --> 58:42.110
shrivel up
because of their imagination.

58:43.070 --> 58:46.280
So do not imagine anything.

58:47.240 --> 58:49.660
You'll become brave as hell.

58:50.330 --> 58:51.960
Now here comes the real thing.

59:24.490 --> 59:28.700
Sir I'm glad
you told me about this place...

59:30.240 --> 59:32.660
..but I haven't even started yet!

59:48.600 --> 59:49.640
Let's go.

01:00:06.610 --> 01:00:07.660
Let's go now.

01:00:08.700 --> 01:00:09.990
Let's fight.

01:00:13.370 --> 01:00:14.500
Let's fight.

01:00:20.550 --> 01:00:22.800
- What a tough guy!
- Your hand.

01:00:24.090 --> 01:00:25.760
I'll chop off your hand.

01:00:27.260 --> 01:00:31.010
You touched Mido's breasts.

01:00:36.100 --> 01:00:37.810
Let's get out of this dump.

01:00:53.830 --> 01:00:56.370
So do you trust me now you bastard?

01:01:00.080 --> 01:01:02.590
It looks hard to accomplish.

01:01:02.750 --> 01:01:04.340
I looked into it.

01:01:04.510 --> 01:01:07.340
The reason the bank
refused to pay $270 million

01:01:07.510 --> 01:01:10.050
was not due to
any building irregularities.

01:01:10.220 --> 01:01:11.930
They have internal problems.

01:01:16.180 --> 01:01:19.560
So I don't think
we'll have any trouble.

01:01:19.730 --> 01:01:25.070
Chairman Choi's
23 clients' shares are at 25% ...

01:01:32.450 --> 01:01:33.870
Dae-su.

01:01:35.240 --> 01:01:36.410
Yeah?

01:01:39.540 --> 01:01:42.460
Did he really say that he'd kill me?

01:01:44.590 --> 01:01:45.420
Yeah.

01:01:46.550 --> 01:01:49.010
Because I'm the woman you love?

01:01:55.010 --> 01:01:56.140
Dae-su.

01:01:58.390 --> 01:01:59.560
What?

01:02:00.730 --> 01:02:03.610
<i>Where is my love?</i>

01:02:05.400 --> 01:02:08.190
<i>I'm getting lonelier in the nights</i>

01:02:11.910 --> 01:02:14.780
<i>The words you send with your eyes</i>

01:02:16.910 --> 01:02:20.000
<i>I can feel with my hand</i>

01:02:21.330 --> 01:02:24.880
<i>So many nights have passed</i>

01:02:26.250 --> 01:02:29.550
<i>My heart is going to you</i>

01:02:31.050 --> 01:02:34.890
<i>As I shed my sad tears</i>

01:02:35.600 --> 01:02:39.640
<i>You're the face I miss.</i>

01:02:44.610 --> 01:02:48.480
They packed up their stuff
and left in a rental car.

01:02:50.530 --> 01:02:54.870
Also Mido called the restaurant
and left her job.

01:02:58.660 --> 01:03:00.910
Let's go after this is done.

01:03:03.330 --> 01:03:05.380
You should get some rest today sir.

01:03:07.420 --> 01:03:09.210
I can't even sleep.

01:03:10.260 --> 01:03:12.010
Because I am lonely.

01:03:12.970 --> 01:03:14.220
Mr Han.

01:03:15.640 --> 01:03:17.560
Do you really think...

01:03:18.850 --> 01:03:21.430
..that Mido has fallen in love
with Oh Dae-su?

01:03:23.600 --> 01:03:24.980
Already?

01:03:45.420 --> 01:03:46.670
Dae-su!

01:03:47.840 --> 01:03:49.300
It hurts so much.

01:03:50.300 --> 01:03:52.510
But I'll endure it.

01:03:54.220 --> 01:03:55.430
You must understand.

01:04:10.690 --> 01:04:13.530
How did you hold out for 15 years?

01:04:14.150 --> 01:04:15.660
There's always a way.

01:04:17.120 --> 01:04:18.950
Do you like it?

01:04:20.620 --> 01:04:22.200
You do like it don't you?

01:04:23.000 --> 01:04:25.120
I want to make you feel good Dae-su.

01:04:53.900 --> 01:04:56.030
<i>You need not worry about the future.</i>

01:04:57.780 --> 01:04:59.200
<i>Imagine nothing.</i>

01:05:10.750 --> 01:05:13.920
<i>I am grateful for</i>
<i>all those years spent in that prison.</i>

01:05:16.510 --> 01:05:20.720
<i>If I was the old Oh Dae-su</i>
<i>would Mido still have liked me?</i>

