01:34:35.020 --> 01:34:36.060
Who are you?

01:34:38.020 --> 01:34:39.650
Do you

01:34:39.810 --> 01:34:41.270
like your clothes?

01:34:42.730 --> 01:34:45.690
<i>And Mido was programmed</i>
<i>to react to the man</i>

01:34:45.860 --> 01:34:47.450
<i>who would say this.</i>

01:34:47.610 --> 01:34:51.160
<i>When she touched your hand</i>
<i>your reaction would be...</i>

01:34:55.200 --> 01:34:58.290
Your gravest mistake
wasn't failing to find the answer.

01:34:59.420 --> 01:35:01.000
If you keep

01:35:01.210 --> 01:35:05.000
asking the wrong questions
you'll never find the right answer.

01:35:05.170 --> 01:35:09.760
It's not
"Why did Woo-jin imprison me?"

01:35:10.180 --> 01:35:12.930
It's "Why did he release me?"

01:35:13.100 --> 01:35:14.970
Once again...

01:35:16.020 --> 01:35:20.100
..why did Woo-jin
release Dae-su after...

01:35:21.770 --> 01:35:23.770
..15 years?

01:37:25.310 --> 01:37:28.610
LAUGH AND THE WORLD LAUGHS
WITH YOU. WEEP AND YOU WEEP
ALONE.

01:39:09.750 --> 01:39:11.040
<i>Mr Han.</i>

01:39:19.970 --> 01:39:21.470
<i>Mr Han!</i>

01:40:02.140 --> 01:40:03.390
Mido...

01:40:10.230 --> 01:40:11.600
Mido doesn't know?

01:40:16.940 --> 01:40:18.990
Why did you hide her there?

01:40:20.990 --> 01:40:24.240
Did you think he'd hate me
just because I cut off his hand?

01:40:24.620 --> 01:40:26.780
Didn't you work out
that it was a trap?

01:40:29.160 --> 01:40:32.370
How can you protect your woman
with that brain?

01:40:33.880 --> 01:40:37.710
I've secretly been raising Mido
since she was three.

01:40:39.130 --> 01:40:41.130
What's wrong with you?

01:40:42.260 --> 01:40:43.890
Mr Park's hand?

01:40:45.680 --> 01:40:46.970
You moron.

01:40:48.140 --> 01:40:52.480
Did you see his new prison? I gave
him that building for his hand!

01:40:52.640 --> 01:40:53.850
Me!

01:41:18.630 --> 01:41:19.840
Dae-su!

01:41:21.880 --> 01:41:23.720
In front of me

01:41:23.930 --> 01:41:26.010
there's some kind of box.

01:41:26.180 --> 01:41:28.010
He's telling me to open it.

01:41:28.640 --> 01:41:30.390
It's the same violet box...

01:41:30.600 --> 01:41:31.560
No!

01:41:32.390 --> 01:41:34.730
No Mido don't.

01:41:34.890 --> 01:41:37.310
Don't open it no matter what.

01:41:37.480 --> 01:41:39.730
Or something terrible will happen.

01:41:39.940 --> 01:41:43.070
What's in it?
You know don't you?

01:41:43.610 --> 01:41:46.070
Mido just wait a little longer.

01:41:46.860 --> 01:41:48.620
Dae-su will be there soon.

01:41:48.780 --> 01:41:51.790
I'll be there very soon.

01:41:53.830 --> 01:41:56.040
Can't you come now?

01:41:58.460 --> 01:41:59.670
I'm scared.

01:41:59.880 --> 01:42:01.840
Little Mido you can wait can't you?

01:42:02.050 --> 01:42:03.170
Yes.

01:42:04.090 --> 01:42:06.380
Very good. Good girl.

01:42:07.510 --> 01:42:11.140
I'll call you back very soon OK?

01:42:26.360 --> 01:42:27.410
Please.

01:42:30.830 --> 01:42:32.540
Don't tell Mido.

01:42:37.290 --> 01:42:38.960
What has she done wrong?

01:42:41.500 --> 01:42:43.050
You know it was all my fault.

01:42:47.180 --> 01:42:48.550
I have...

01:42:50.140 --> 01:42:52.310
..committed an unforgivable sin...

01:42:53.310 --> 01:42:55.100
..against your sister.

01:42:56.980 --> 01:42:59.060
And I also...

01:43:00.610 --> 01:43:01.980
..did you wrong.

01:43:03.520 --> 01:43:04.570
But...

01:43:06.490 --> 01:43:08.570
..please leave Mido alone.

01:43:14.410 --> 01:43:15.450
If by any chance...

01:43:17.000 --> 01:43:19.000
..Mido finds out the truth

01:43:20.000 --> 01:43:22.000
you son of a bitch

01:43:22.630 --> 01:43:26.260
I'll tear you limb from limb.

01:43:27.470 --> 01:43:31.550
And your remains will never be found.

01:43:31.720 --> 01:43:33.100
Why?

01:43:33.260 --> 01:43:35.930
Because I'm going
to swallow every last bit.

01:43:38.480 --> 01:43:39.600
Woo-jin!

01:43:40.560 --> 01:43:43.020
Please sir I made a mistake.

01:43:43.360 --> 01:43:46.650
Please forget what I said.

01:43:46.820 --> 01:43:49.150
Sir! Woo-jin!

01:43:50.110 --> 01:43:54.200
We're Evergreen Old Boys remember?

01:43:55.240 --> 01:44:01.290
<i>With the energy</i>
<i>of a green pine tree</i>

01:44:04.460 --> 01:44:08.050
<i>The Great Sangnok High...</i>

01:44:11.590 --> 01:44:14.760
I'll do whatever you want.

01:44:14.970 --> 01:44:17.100
I'll do anything. I beg you.

01:44:17.770 --> 01:44:22.940
Woo-jin if you want me
to be your dog I will!

01:44:23.100 --> 01:44:27.020
From this moment on
I am Woo-jin's dog!

01:44:27.190 --> 01:44:28.230
I'm your bitch.

01:44:34.870 --> 01:44:37.030
Look I'm wagging my tail.

01:44:37.660 --> 01:44:40.580
I'm a dog. I'll guard your house.

01:44:40.750 --> 01:44:43.370
I'll be your slave.

01:46:51.040 --> 01:46:52.500
The box...

01:46:58.260 --> 01:46:59.680
..just leave it closed.

01:47:10.560 --> 01:47:11.610
Now...

01:47:14.730 --> 01:47:17.030
..what will I live for?

01:48:19.510 --> 01:48:20.680
<i>Dae-su.</i>

01:48:21.470 --> 01:48:23.140
<i>It hurts so much.</i>

01:48:23.930 --> 01:48:25.760
<i>But I'll endure it.</i>

01:48:26.850 --> 01:48:28.220
<i>You must understand.</i>

01:48:52.420 --> 01:48:55.710
My sister and I loved each other
despite everything.

01:49:00.210 --> 01:49:01.880
Can you two do the same?

01:49:45.380 --> 01:49:46.220
Soo-ah.

01:50:02.240 --> 01:50:03.440
Woo-jin.

01:50:05.320 --> 01:50:07.320
I know you've always been afraid.

01:50:10.160 --> 01:50:12.910
So just let go of me.

01:50:29.970 --> 01:50:32.850
Please remember me.

01:50:41.360 --> 01:50:44.070
I have no regrets. Do you?

01:51:29.610 --> 01:51:33.450
<i>This is the whole adventure</i>
<i>of my life until now.</i>

01:51:33.620 --> 01:51:37.160
<i>Thank you for listening</i>
<i>to this terrible story to the end.</i>

01:51:37.870 --> 01:51:42.290
<i>I trust that you will understand</i>
<i>my sending a letter</i>

01:51:42.460 --> 01:51:46.090
<i>instead of talking to you in person.</i>

01:51:46.260 --> 01:51:48.170
<i>This is because</i>
<i>I have no tongue.</i>

01:51:48.340 --> 01:51:51.010
To be honest
there's no reason I should help you.

01:51:56.890 --> 01:51:58.270
But there was one thing.

01:51:59.480 --> 01:52:01.770
I was touched by this last sentence.

01:52:03.820 --> 01:52:09.450
EVEN THOUGH
I'M NO BETTER THAN A BEAST

01:52:09.610 --> 01:52:13.120
DON'T I HAVE THE RIGHT TO LIVE?

01:52:16.040 --> 01:52:19.040
The hypnosis may go wrong
and distort your memories.

01:52:20.960 --> 01:52:22.250
Do you want to proceed?

01:52:43.480 --> 01:52:45.310
If you're ready...

01:52:47.150 --> 01:52:49.150
..look at that tree.

01:53:06.130 --> 01:53:07.380
The tree...

01:53:08.420 --> 01:53:11.470
..is slowly changing
into a concrete pillar.

01:53:20.100 --> 01:53:24.020
You're now
inside Lee Woo-jin's penthouse.

01:53:25.150 --> 01:53:26.810
<i>It's a dreary night.</i>

01:53:30.110 --> 01:53:32.900
<i>The sound of your footsteps</i>
<i>crossing to the window</i>

01:53:33.070 --> 01:53:34.910
<i>fills the room.</i>

01:53:49.050 --> 01:53:52.590
<i>When I ring my bell...</i>

01:53:54.050 --> 01:53:56.930
<i>..you'll split into two people.</i>

01:54:01.060 --> 01:54:04.440
<i>One person doesn't know</i>
<i>your secret.: Oh Dae-su.</i>

01:54:05.690 --> 01:54:08.520
<i>The one who knows your secret</i>
<i>is the monster.</i>

01:54:09.980 --> 01:54:12.280
<i>When I ring the bell again</i>

01:54:12.440 --> 01:54:15.530
<i>the monster will turn around</i>
<i>and start walking.</i>

01:54:20.370 --> 01:54:26.170
<i>With each step</i>
<i>he will age by one year.</i>

01:54:26.370 --> 01:54:29.250
<i>When he reaches 70</i>
<i>the monster will die.</i>

01:54:29.840 --> 01:54:31.340
<i>There's no need to worry.</i>

01:54:32.340 --> 01:54:35.050
<i>It will be a very peaceful death.</i>

01:54:42.720 --> 01:54:44.230
<i>Now good luck to you.</i>

01:55:26.890 --> 01:55:28.940
What's going on?

01:55:29.900 --> 01:55:31.940
Look at you.

01:56:01.090 --> 01:56:02.720
Who were you with?

01:56:58.650 --> 01:57:00.150
I love you...

01:57:01.280 --> 01:57:02.530
..Dae-su..

